! conclusion: Composition (鹽) is not concatenation but the recognition that latent potential (鹵) and stabilizing container (皿) are available under the same decomposition regime (部). Make the symbolic operations patterns perform implicitly explicit as the futonic loop: input · decompose · articulate · compose · sense · regulate · act · evaluate.

  + context: Futon-theory patterns presuppose a shared vocabulary and a recognition loop but rarely name them. Futonic logic declares the core symbols as roles (not definitions) and states the composition rule, so patterns can be checked and composed rather than merely juxtaposed. The full specification — vocabulary, grounding tables against actual usage, axiom A7, the three-time (既/化/應·債) ledger, and boundary rule 味→未@0 — is at @essay-source.

  + IF:
    You are composing futon artefacts — patterns, proof-paths, missions, sessions — and want the composition to be generative rather than mere juxtaposition.

  + HOWEVER:
    If you fix meaning before structure is verified (premature semantic collapse) or treat composition as concatenation, symbols cannot compose: potential (鹵) and container (皿) sit adjacent without generating. This was the Agency/Forum/Drawbridge failure — 鹵 present, 皿 (the recording protocol) absent — leaving systems 非死非活: responsive but not self-sustaining.

  + THEN:
    Run the futonic loop: take a configuration (象), choose a decomposition regime (部), articulate it (咅); if a (⿱ 鹵 皿) composition forms and both terms are perceivable, sense salience (香) and regulate (🔮), then act within 未知 and evaluate by felt difference (味); else set down (捨). Perceive the interval honestly (間) before composing (axiom A7); at a boundary, let 味→未 collapse and contain (戒/圍/包) rather than force.

  + BECAUSE:
    Salience is the moment an agent perceives that 鹵 and 皿 compose under the current 部. Without a container composition cannot form; without composition salience cannot emerge; without salience agents cannot perceive whether their coordination is working. The loop is the abstract form of the PSR→PUR cycle and the derivation xenotype alike, and it keeps the three-time ledger honest: 既 authorises, 化 fires, (應 . 債) is owed.

  + NEXT-STEPS:
    - Extend the vocabulary as new symbols emerge from practice — the specification is open, not closed.
    - Verify A7 is consistent with A1–A5 (complementary scope, no contradiction).
    - Connect to futon3a search: 香 operations map to notions/compass similarity queries.
    - Full specification, grounding tables, and worked loops live in the essay at @essay-source (to be published on hyperreal.enterprises).
    - Companion pattern: futon-theory/the-woven-form — the root-metaphor (composition = spinning) this vocabulary grounds.
